    "C. Optimizing Generative Model PerformancePrompts are the way of communication with currently popular AI applications based on LLM's like ChatGPT.",
    "The quality of outputs from a conversational LLM is due to the quality of the prompts.",
    "Prompt patterns systematically guide LLMs enhancing interaction and task automation, providing a reusable solution framework to recurring problems.",
    "They provide a structured approach to customizing LLM output and interactions.",
    "Prompt Engineering is the art of crafting effective prompts to guide the responses of a machine learning model to achieve desired outputs or behaviors."
